      "role": "user",
      "content": "small steps? i don't see how. even if i recycle or whatever, the big corporations and governments are just gonna keep burning everything down. it feels like trying to put out a forest fire with a water pistol. it honestly just feels like a lie to say we can \"make a difference\" when the math literally says we're past the point of no return. it's just a way to keep people productive while everything falls apart.",
